{
  "stem": "1413.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where are those letters?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where are those letters?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a man in Amsterdam, in the Netherlands-- I think Amsterdam-- he wrote 11 books about the war, about the Jewish and all.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My sister-in-law's-- my sister-in-law's husband who worked for the underground, I told you a couple of times-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] my sister-in-law was asked by-- and she kept the letters.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She kept the pieces, the [INAUDIBLE] and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on there was a Belgian guy, Armand Felinder-- he wrote my writing on his card, so that the handwriting was his.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he also worked in the [NON-ENGLISH], and he a case of his tools.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when he received a package, he put it in the case and he told me-- that he couldn't hand it to me because they could have killed him if they saw me giving him, giving me something.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I took it out of this tool case.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He told me where it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] My sister-in-law, then, oh-- 11 times-- so the man who wrote the books asked my sister-in-law if he could have those letters for the War Documentation in the Netherlands.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she wrote me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, go ahead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So the War Documentation from the Netherlands have those letters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One day, about seven, eight years ago, my daughter went to the Netherlands-- where she is right now, also-- she went to the War Documentation, and she asked if she could see it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She saw it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was just in a drawer-- it was not on display.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That burned me up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they made copies for her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But copies they typed the words that I had written in-- in Blechhammer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They typed up all Dutch words on paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
